snippet.title: Helskate - Official Reveal Trailer | Day of the Devs 2023
snippet.description:
Helskate is an action rogue-lite skateboarding game where players will grind, perform tricks, and chain combos to power up their attacks to slay the monsters of Vertheim. Use weapons and gear to best suit your playstyle and upgrade your abilities. Helskate is coming soon to PC.

#IGN #SummerOfGaming
